Class SettingsDialog

java.lang.Object
javafx.scene.control.Dialog<javafx.scene.control.ButtonType>
com.comp2042.SettingsDialog
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.event.EventTarget
public class SettingsDialog extends javafx.scene.control.Dialog<javafx.scene.control.ButtonType>
Dialog window for game settings configuration. Allows users to adjust ghost piece visibility, music settings, volume, and background picture.
